    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what u mean about the instability. but some people argue that the humanitarian aspect was actually a huge win—like, if the west hadn't stepped in, there would have been a massive massacre in benghazi or sitra. isnt it more of a moral success even if the politics went south?",
